def test_dynamic_like_collect(self):
        try:
            # 初始化发现页操作类（传入self即可复用所有minium对象）
            find_page = FindPage(self)

            # 链式调用公共方法，逻辑清晰
            find_page.goto_find_page()

            # 需要判断是不是在推荐菜单
            menu_name = self.page.get_element(menu_active_element, max_timeout=max_timeout)
            menu_name_text = menu_name.text

            if menu_name_text != menu_dynamic_name:
                menu_list = self.page.get_elements(menu_element, max_timeout=max_timeout)
                # 点击推荐
                for i in menu_list:
                    if i.text == menu_dynamic_name:
                        i.tap()
                        self.logger.info(f"已切换到 {i.text} 菜单")

            """点赞 like"""
            like_status = self.page.get_element(dynamic_list_unlike_icon_element, max_timeout=max_timeout)
            # 先判断是否是 未点赞
            if like_status.attribute("src") == [dynamic_list_unlike_icon_src]:
                # 如果是未点赞 先点赞 like
                unlike_icon = self.page.get_element(dynamic_list_unlike_icon_element, max_timeout=max_timeout)
                unlike_icon.tap()

                time.sleep(1)

                new_like_status = self.page.get_element(dynamic_list_unlike_icon_element, max_timeout=max_timeout)

                if new_like_status.attribute("src") == [dynamic_list_like_icon_src]:
                    self.logger.info(f"点击 {dynamic_list_unlike_icon_name} 成功")
                else:
                    self.logger.info(f"点击 {dynamic_list_unlike_icon_name} 失败")

                time.sleep(1)
            else:
                # 如果是已点赞 取消点赞
                like_icon = self.page.get_element(dynamic_list_unlike_icon_element, max_timeout=max_timeout)
                like_icon.tap()

                time.sleep(1)

                new_like_status = self.page.get_element(dynamic_list_unlike_icon_element, max_timeout=max_timeout)

                if new_like_status.attribute("src") == [dynamic_list_unlike_icon_src]:
                    self.logger.info(f"点击 {dynamic_list_like_icon_name} 成功")
                else:
                    self.logger.info(f"点击 {dynamic_list_like_icon_name} 失败")

            timestamp = time.strftime("%H%M%S")
            self.capture(f"点赞+收藏后_{timestamp}", region=self.page)

            """收藏 collect"""
            collect_status = self.page.get_element(dynamic_list_uncollect_icon_element, max_timeout=max_timeout)

            # 先判断是否是 未收藏
            if collect_status.attribute("src") == [dynamic_list_uncollect_icon_src]:
                # 如果是未收藏 先收藏 collect
                uncollect_icon = self.page.get_element(dynamic_list_uncollect_icon_element, max_timeout=max_timeout)
                uncollect_icon.tap()

                time.sleep(1)

                new_collect_status = self.page.get_element(dynamic_list_uncollect_icon_element, max_timeout=max_timeout)

                if new_collect_status.attribute("src") == [dynamic_list_collect_icon_src]:
                    self.logger.info(f"点击 {dynamic_list_uncollect_icon_name} 成功")
                else:
                    self.logger.info(f"点击 {dynamic_list_uncollect_icon_name} 失败")

                time.sleep(1)
            else:
                # 如果是已收藏 取消收藏
                collect_icon = self.page.get_element(dynamic_list_uncollect_icon_element, max_timeout=max_timeout)
                collect_icon.tap()

                time.sleep(1)

                new_collect_status = self.page.get_element(dynamic_list_uncollect_icon_element, max_timeout=max_timeout)

                if new_collect_status.attribute("src") == [dynamic_list_uncollect_icon_src]:
                    self.logger.info(f"点击 {dynamic_list_collect_icon_name} 成功")
                else:
                    self.logger.info(f"点击 {dynamic_list_collect_icon_name} 失败")

            timestamp = time.strftime("%H%M%S")
            self.capture(f"点赞+收藏后_{timestamp}", region=self.page)

        except Exception as e:
            self.logger.error(f"点赞、收藏失败：{str(e)}")
            # 异常时截图
            timestamp = time.strftime("%H%M%S")
            self.capture(f"点赞、收藏失败_{timestamp}")
            raise

        time.sleep(2)
